# Research: Fast-Model Candidates for the Conversational Loop

## Question

TTFT is ~70% of perceived response latency (median 1.28s, p95 5.4s on
anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.6 via OpenRouter). Which 2-3 candidates should the
A/B trial? Constraints: available via OpenRouter (the approved voice path),
strong function-calling (the agent is tool-heavy), low TTFT with streaming,
good at terse persona adherence. Check published TTFT/latency data (OpenRouter
throughput stats, provider docs), price per call, and any voice-agent
practitioner reports. Deliverable: comparison asset with a ranked
recommendation.
